<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Actualy it's impossible to add support of other scheme than http and https without duplicate Zend_Uri class, and so other subclasses because their constructors are protected and extends Zend_Uri.</p>

<p>I suggest to make a table likes :</p>

<p>protected $schemeClasses = array(
  'http' =&gt; 'Zend_Uri_Http',
  'https' =&gt; 'Zend_Uri_Http',
);</p>

<p>And some methods like addSchemmeClass($scheme, $classname)</p>

